UC30 ..> UC26 : <<trigger>>
UC31 ..> UC24 : <<trigger>>

note right of UC1
  Captures exercise activities
  with duration, type, intensity
  and optional distance
end note

note right of UC7
  Allows setting daily, weekly
  or monthly activity targets
  with multiple metrics
end note

note right of UC13
  Documents behavioral incidents
  with severity, triggers, and
  recommended actions
end note

note bottom of UC18
  Central hub showing activity
  summary, goal progress, and
  recent sessions
end note

note bottom of UC28
  Automatically calculates based
  on pet profile, activity type,
  duration, and intensity
end note

note bottom of UC29
  Tracks progress against goals
  and triggers completion alerts
  when targets are met
end note

note bottom of UC30
  Identifies patterns, triggers,
  and trends in pet behavior for
  proactive intervention
end note

note bottom of UC31
  Publishes domain events for
  ExerciseSessionLogged,
  ExerciseGoalSet, and
  BehaviorIncidentLogged
end note

note bottom of UC32
  Provides AI-generated insights
  based on activity and behavior
  data analysis
end note

@enduml
